  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37280</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_008_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あれ？　なんかヘンくね？
さっきまで戦い疲れてたのに……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? Isn't this kinda weird? We were exhausted from the fight just a moment ago...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <StructId>1</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37708</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_008_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>体力が回復してる？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Our stamina has recovered?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <StructId>2</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37820</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_008_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エッヘヘ〜ン！　アルベルト様が教えてやるだーよ。
それも『なりきり士』の力のひとつだ、&lt;MEL&gt;&lt;MEL&gt;∀</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hehehe~! Lord Albert will teach you! That's also one of the powers of the 'Imitator', &lt;MEL&gt;&lt;MEL&gt;∀</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <StructId>3</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>25</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39716</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_008_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ノルン様の加護ある場所なら、
大地の力で体力も全回復だ〜〜よ♪</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If you're in a place blessed by Lady Norn, the power of the earth will fully restore your stamina~♪</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <StructId>4</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>25</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40588</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_008_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おまえがそんなでけーずーたい隠して、
手伝わないから疲れるんだっての！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're hiding that big body of yours and not helping, that's why you're tired!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <StructId>5</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41560</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_008_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はん、おら、戦ってもええだが、衣装がボロボロになるだど！
偉そうなこと言って。おめぇが使えねぇからだろ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hmph, I could fight, but my outfit would get all torn up! You're acting all high and mighty, but it's because you're useless!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <StructId>6</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>25</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43076</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_008_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;DIO&gt;、アルベルトさんも……
やめてください</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;DIO&gt;, Mr. Albert... please stop.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <StructId>7</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44352</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_008_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あう〜〜ん、&lt;MEL&gt;&lt;MEL&gt;ぅ、言ってやってほしいだ。
このクソぼうずに、おらがどれだけ大変かっちゅーの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Aww~ &lt;MEL&gt;&lt;MEL&gt;, please tell him. Tell this little brat how hard I have it!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <StructId>8</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>25</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46300</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_008_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>こんのぉ〜……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You little...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <StructId>9</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46564</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_008_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>っつーことで、ダンジョンから外に出れば、
体力が全快だで、いちいち寝る必要もないだーよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So, if you leave the dungeon, your stamina will fully recover, and you won't need to sleep every time.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <StructId>10</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>25</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48076</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_008_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……誰に向かって
言ってんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Who do you think you're talking to?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <StructId>11</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
